  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966430/extras/gameplay_gif.GIF?t=1741004250\" /></span><br><br>Would you survive a panic attack? Test your limits in this <strong>anxiety-inducing twin-stick shooter</strong> and <strong>prove that you are the most resilient person in the world</strong>.<br><strong>Blast away the Intrusive Thoughts</strong> using your Inner Weapon and survive the nightmares to make it through.<br>It's never been so difficult to calm down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966430/extras/f8899a32a46c9a603ea17faa911d791e.avif?t=1741004250\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Choose your Inner Weapon</strong> to destroy the Intrusive Thoughts.<br></li><li> <strong>All</strong> the Inner Weapons are <strong>completely unique</strong>: abilities, shooting, speed and accuracy are different from each other.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966430/extras/269e85f532aad8f2e496372a7d8e11ab.avif?t=1741004250\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966430/extras/19ec559a18e977bfae00ce781dc06dc9.avif?t=1741004250\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>The higher the BPM, the stronger, faster the Intrusive Thoughts become, the quicker they’ll spawn and higher will be the points you get.</strong> If you can survive high BPM, you will be for sure the best.<br></li><li> <strong>You'll hear the heart pounding</strong> and the mind degeneration, thanks to the <strong>immersive sounds</strong>.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966430/extras/a43bb0649533a3af156ece8540ffa85c.avif?t=1741004250\" width=600 height=119 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966430/extras/discord.GIF?t=1741004250\" /></span>",
